<HEADLINE>
FRANKS ATTACKS DODD'S VOTING RECORD IN DEBATE 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION NOTICE: also sent in category `a') 
(bl) 
 By JULIAN E. BARNES   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
