   EXCLUSIVE-KENYA-BOMB (New York) _ Federal prosecutors have filed
secret charges against a former sergeant in the U.S. Special Forces
who is suspected of switching sides in the war against terrorism
and joining the global campaign to attack Americans mounted by the
Saudi exile Osama bin Laden. By Benjamin Weiser.
</P>
<P>
   (ART ADV: Photo [NYT37) has been sent to NYT photo clients.)
</P>
