   _ Western Governors University: wgu.edu/wgu/index.html
</P>
<P>
   _ ``Digital Diploma Mills'' paper by David Noble:
firstmonday.dk/issues/issue3_1/noble/
</P>
<P>
   -------
</P>
<P>
   (Pamela Mendels, a Manhattan-based writer, covers education,
government, censorship and civil rights issues for CyberTimes.)
