<P>
   &UR; EDITORS: Nowadays more and more people are working from home _ and
from home pages on the Internet. The New York Times Syndicate, in
recognition of Home-Based Business Week from Oct. 11-17, looks at
the evolving workplace in the age of cyberspace.
</P>
<P>
   _ STARTING A SUCCESSFUL HOME BUSINESS
</P>
<P>
   _ IS WORKING AT HOME RIGHT FOR YOU?
</P>
<P>
   _ BUYING THE RIGHT EQUIPMENT FOR YOUR HOME OFFICE
</P>
