<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-30 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5749 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JOHN-GLENN-PROFILE-NY     10-30 2104
