<P>
   NYMARATHON-KENYANS (New York) _ Of the 32,000 runners in
Sunday's marathon, 12,000 will be first-timers, and one of those
might actually win. Peter Githuka of Kenya is one, and Josef
Kiriuki of Kenya is another. By Jere Longman.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-REPORT (Undated) _ Saturday's top games. By Frank Litsky.
</P>
