<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-30 15:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5947 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FINANCE-HOOKER-BOS &LR;      10-30 1112
