   AUS-FOOTBALL _ AISD has something no other Central Texas
district has _ two women who are football coaches. Lori Frels
coaches the seventh grade B team at Bailey Middle School and says
her boys look to her for the mothers' touch her male comrades don't
have. The other female football coach is at Burnet Middle in
Austin. We profile these women who work in a field that
traditionally has not been open to women. (Alford, Austin
American-Statesman) WITH PHOTOS
</P>
<P>
