<HEADLINE>
BIG MONEY POURS INTO CALIFORNIA ELECTION 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Filed in ``a'' and ``p'' category)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By CHUCK FINNIE  
 c.1998 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
