</P>
<P>
   MARIANNE WILLIAMSON Born:Resides:
</P>
<P>
   Accomplishments: Oprah Winfrey's show transformed her virtually
overnight into a celebrity of the human potential movement.
</P>
<P>
   Latest book:Excerpt:Web site:
</P>
<P>
   Whole Life Expo Topic: .
</P>
