   CORRECTION:
</P>
<P>
   An article by the New York Times News Service on Friday about
Ali A. Mohamed, a former U.S. Army sergeant who has been charged
with involvement in Osama bin Laden's global war against Americans,
referred incorrectly to his military assignment. Mohamed served as
a supply sergeant and assistant instructor on the staff of the John
