the United States gather here Sunday for the ``Pro Bowl'' of
anti-terrorist and security forces competitions. Instead of
tackling runners or throwing footballs, the nearly 200 uniformed
personnel will compete with rifles, machine guns and grenade
launchers. By SIG CHRISTENSON. (Already filed.)
