<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-30 20:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6577 &Cx1f; tta-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ECON-REPORT-ART-365&AMP;A     10-30 1326
</HEADER>
<BODY>
